        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Dreams of finding lost treasure almost came true recently.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.25,
      "endTime": 20.35
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "A new machine called 'The Revealer' has been invented",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.36,
      "endTime": 25.27
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "and it has been used to detect gold which has been buried in the ground.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.28,
      "endTime": 32.06,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The machine was used in a cave near the seashore where--it is said--pirates used to hide gold.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 32.07,
      "endTime": 41.96,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The pirates would often bury gold in the cave and then fail to collect it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.97,
      "endTime": 49.06,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Armed with the new machine, a search party went into the cave hoping to find buried treasure.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 49.07,
      "endTime": 57.24
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The leader of the party was examining the soil near the entrance to the cave when the machine showed that there was gold under the ground.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.25,
      "endTime": 68.5,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Very excited, the party dug a hole two feet deep.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 68.51,
      "endTime": 74.13,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "Very",
            "label": "程度副词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They finally found a small gold coin which was almost worthless.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.14,
      "endTime": 80.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The party then searched the whole cave thoroughly but did not find anything except an empty tin trunk.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.66,
      "endTime": 91.2,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
